    "quiz_mode_title": "Pick right ajụjụ ọnụ ọnọdụ",
    "quiz_mode_text": "Họrọ gịnị nke otu ajụjụ ọnụ bụ maka. Exit Ticket checks today’s mmụta. Pre-Check probes prior knowledge before teaching na surfaces gaps as concept kaadị na otu one-pịa \"Explain na klas\" AI broadcast. Formative Check bụ otu ngwa ngwa mid-nkuzi pulse. Spaced Review tracks nke ọ bụla nwa akwụkwọ’s cross-nnọkọ retention na otu per-concept sparkline. nke ọ bụla ọnọdụ tunes prompts, ihe-type mix, na na-ekwu okwu dashboard layout.",
