      "iep_goal_bank_fraction_specific": "🎯 Ụlọ Akụ Ebumnuche IEP — akọwapụtara maka nkebi",
      "pre_formatted_smart_goals_for_iep_team": "Ebumnuche SMART e haziri maka otu IEP. Ebumnuche ọ bụla na-ejikọ na ụkpụrụ CCSS, na-atụ aro isi mmalite data nnyocha-ọganihu n'ime AlloFlow, ma depụta ndozi nkịtị. Detuo ma megharịa maka nwa akwụkwọ gị.",
      "show_accommodations_and_progress_monit": "Gosi ndozi na nnyocha ọganihu",
