      "dangerous_if_you_can_smell_nh_the_conc": "Ize ndụ! Ọ bụrụ na ị nwere ike ịnụ isi NH₃, ọnụ ọgụgụ nwere ike ịgafe oke dị mma (25 ppm). Kọntaktị ogologo oge na-akpata ọkụ kemịkal n'ụzọ iku ume. NH₃ nke >300 ppm nwere ike ịbụ ihe na-egbu egbu.",
      "someone_brought_bleach": "Mmadụ wetara bleach!",
      "a_classmate_suggests_cleaning_the_benc": "Mgbe ị ka mepere ngwọta ammonia, onye klas gị na-atụ aro ka e jiri bleach hichaa bench.",
      "stop_them_immediately_bleach_ammonia_t": "Kwụsị ha ozugbo! Bleach + ammonia = gas chloramine nsi",
      "life_saving_action_naocl_2nh_2nh_cl_ch": "Omume nzọpụta ndụ! NaOCl + 2NH₃ → 2NH₂Cl (chloramine) — gas nsi na-akpata mmebi iku ume siri ike. Nke a bụ otu n'ime ngwakọta mberede kacha dị ize ndụ n'ụlọ nyocha. Mgbe niile mee ka kemịkal niile dị nhaghị ma tufuo ha tupu iji ngwọta nhicha ọ bụla.",
