      "extremely_dangerous_mixing_bleach_naoc": "Ize ndụ nke ukwuu! Ịgwakọta bleach (NaOCl) na ammonia na-emepụta gas chloramine nsi. Ọ kpatala ọnwụ n'ụlọ nyocha na ụlọ. Egwakọtala bleach na kemịkal ọ bụla ọzọ ma ọlị.",
