      "platte_river_ne": "Platte River, NE",
      "600_000_sandhill_cranes_gather_here_ea": "Sandhill Cranes 600,000 na-ezukọ ebe a n'oge opupu ihe ubi ọ bụla — otu n'ime ihe ngosi kacha mara mma nke okike",
      "great_salt_lake": "Great Salt Lake",
