      "l_d_measures_aerodynamic_efficiency_a_": "L/D na-atụ arụmọrụ aerodynamic. L/D dị elu pụtara mbuli karịa n'otu nkeji ịdọkpụ. Albatross na-enweta nha L/D nke usoro ",
