      "greenland_ice_sheet_collapse": "Ọdịda nke Mpempe Ice Greenland",
      "the_greenland_ice_sheet_holds_enough_w": "Mpempe ice Greenland nwere mmiri zuru ezu iji welie ọkwa oké osimiri mita 7 (23 ft). Na ~1.5°C na-adịgide, mgbaze na-aghọ nke a na-apụghị ịgbanwe kemgbe narị afọ ruo puku afọ.",
      "amoc_collapse_gulf_stream": "Ọdịda AMOC (Gulf Stream)",
