      "amazon_rainforest_dieback": "Mbelata nke Ọhịa Mmiri Amazon",
      "the_amazon_generates_half_its_own_rain": "Amazon na-emepụta ọkara mmiri ozuzo nke ya. Site na igbutu ọhịa 20–25% + okpomọkụ na-arịwanye elu, ọ dị ihe egwu ịtụgharị site n'ọhịa mmiri ruo savanna. Ụfọdụ nnyocha na-egosi na oke dị nso na 2°C na ọnụọgụ igbutu ọhịa ugbu a.",
      "permafrost_methane_release": "Ntọhapụ Methane Permafrost",
