      "west_antarctic_ice_sheet": "Mpempe Ice Ọdịda Anyanwụ Antarctica",
      "marine_based_ice_sheets_anchored_below": "Mpempe ice dabeere n'oké osimiri nke a rapaara n'okpuru ọkwa oké osimiri. Mmiri oké osimiri na-ekpo ọkụ na-eripịa ha site n'okpuru. Glacier Thwaites (“Doomsday Glacier”) bụ isi ihe egwu. Ọdịda ga-eme ka ọkwa oké osimiri rịgoo mita 3.3 (11 ft).",
      "boreal_forest_die_off": "Ọnwụ nke Ọhịa Boreal",
      "northern_coniferous_forests_russia_can": "Ọhịa conifer ugwu (Russia, Canada, Scandinavia) nọ n'okpuru nrụgide site na ọkụ, ebe mkpịsị osisi, na ọkụ ọhịa. Ntụgharị zuru ezu ruo ala ahịhịa nwere ike ịhapụ carbon dị ukwuu echekwara.",
      "gulf_of_maine_rapid_warming": "Ọkụ Ngwa Ngwa nke Gulf of Maine",
      "the_gulf_of_maine_has_warmed_faster_th": "Gulf of Maine ekpola ọkụ ngwa ngwa karịa 99% nke oké osimiri ụwa kemgbe 1980 — ihe dị ka 0.5°F kwa afọ iri, ihe dị ka 3× nke nkezi oké osimiri ụwa. Iyi oyi Labrador adaala mba ka mmiri ọkụ Gulf Stream na-eru ugwu karịa, na-ahazigharị netwọọkụ nri n'oge dị adị site na ntọala. Obodo ụsọ oké osimiri Penobscot, Passamaquoddy, Maliseet, na Mi’kmaq edekọọla mgbanwe ndị a n'ihe ndekọ ọnụ ọtụtụ afọ tupu satịlaịtị kwadoro.",
