      "challenge_complete": "Ọ Emechaala Aṅụrị!",
      "206_bones_support_protection_movement_": "Ọkpụkpụ 206 — nkwado, nchekwa, mmegharị, nchekwa mineral, mmepụta ọbara.",
      "houses_meninges_brain_and_cranial_nerv": "Ọ na-ebu meninges, ụbụrụ, na oghere akwara ozi isi. Njikọ (coronal, sagittal, lambdoid) na-ejikọta mgbe nwatakịrị gbara afọ 2.",
      "ribs_1_12": "Ọgịrịga (1-12)",
