      "all_cards": "Kaadị niile:",
      "cards_are_designed_to_be_printed_and_u": "💡 E mere kaadị ka e bipụta ha ma jiri ha mee ihe pụọ na ihuenyo. Ezigbo manipulatives anụ ahụ ka na-emeri ndị virtual maka K-2 — kinesthetic loop dị mkpa. ",
      "the_app_gives_you_every_manipulative_o": "App na-enye gị MANIPULATIVE ỌBỤLA n'aka, ọbụlagodi mgbe kit anụ ahụ anọghị n'ime ụlọ.",
      "faq": "❓ FAQ",
      "shortcuts": "⌨ Shortcuts",
      "pitfalls": "⚠ Ọnyà",
      "about": "ℹ Gbasara",
      "keyboard_shortcuts": "Keyboard shortcuts:",
      "treating_manipulatives_as_filler_not_i": "Iwere manipulatives dị ka \"mejupụta oge\" ọ bụghị nkuzi",
      "common_mistake_handing_out_blocks_and_": "Ndudue a na-emekarị: ikesa blocks wee pụọ. Na-enweghị nkuzi doro anya na-EJIKỌ manipulative na symbol, ụmụ akwụkwọ na-egwurikarị egwuregwu ahụ ma ghara ịmụta ihe ọhụrụ. Mechie nnọkọ manipulative ọ bụla mgbe niile na: \"Gosi m n'akwụkwọ ihe ị mere.\"",
      "keeping_students_on_the_concrete_stage": "Ịhapụ ụmụ akwụkwọ na nzọụkwụ concrete ogologo oge",
      "a_4th_grader_who_still_needs_blocks_fo": "Nwa akwụkwọ grade 4 nke ka CHỌRỌ blocks maka 23 + 47 nwere nsogbu. Blocks bụ scaffold; ọ bụrụ na a wepụghị ha, fluency adịghị eto. Gaa na representational (foto) ruo grade 2-3, ruo abstract (symbols) ruo grade 3-4. Laghachi na concrete naanị maka concepts ọhụrụ.",
      "skipping_the_representational_stage": "Ịwụfe nzọụkwụ representational",
      "most_rushed_teachers_go_from_blocks_st": "Ọtụtụ ndị nkuzi na-eme ngwa ngwa na-esi na blocks gaa ozugbo na \"ugbu a dee 4 + 5 = 9.\" Nke ahụ na-awụfe nzọụkwụ iconic (ise dots, number lines, arrays). Witzel, Mercer & Miller (2003) chọpụtara na oghere ahụ bụ ebe ọtụtụ ndị na-amụ ihe na-ada. Tinye nzọụkwụ foto mgbe niile.",
      "letting_students_always_work_alone": "Ịhapụ ụmụ akwụkwọ ka ha na-arụ ọrụ naanị ha mgbe niile",
      "manipulative_work_without_talk_is_half": "Ọrụ manipulative na-enweghị OKWU bụ ọkara uru ya. Kepụta ụmụ akwụkwọ abụọ abụọ; chọọ ka ha kwuo ihe ha na-eme n'ọnụ. Ikwu ya n'ọnụ BỤ nzọụkwụ nkwado nke na-akpụga omume site na \"mkpịsị aka maara\" ruo \"isi maara.\"",
      "confusing_speed_with_understanding": "Ịgwakọta ọsọ na nghọta",
      "timed_fact_fluency_drills_can_make_stu": "Drills fact-fluency nwere oge nwere ike ime ka ụmụ akwụkwọ dịkwuo ọsọ na procedures ha na-aghọtaghị (lee nnyocha \"math anxiety\": Boaler 2014). Ọrụ manipulative nwayọ ADỊGHỊ ala karịa ọrụ akwụkwọ ọsọ maka K-3.",
      "mismatching_manipulative_to_standard": "Ekwekọghị manipulative na standard",
      "don_t_use_the_abacus_to_teach_fraction": "Ejila abacus kuzie fractions. Ejila pattern blocks kuzie place value. Maapụ Curriculum na-egosi manipulative na-edozi CCSS ole — malite ebe ahụ.",
      "praising_effort_but_not_strategy": "Ito mgbalị mana ọ bụghị strategy",
      "saying_great_job_rewards_completion_sa": "Ikwu \"ọrụ ọma!\" na-akwụ ụgwọ maka imecha. Ikwu \"Ahụrụ m na ị nwaara trapezoids 3 tupu ị gbanwee gaa na triangles 6 — gịnị mere ka ị gbanwee?\" na-akwụ ụgwọ maka echiche. Kwuo kpọmkwem.",
      "ignoring_student_invented_strategies": "Ileghara strategies ụmụ akwụkwọ chepụtara anya",
      "a_student_who_shows_8_5_as_9_4_because": "Nwa akwụkwọ na-egosi 8 + 5 dị ka \"9 + 4\" (n'ihi na o were 1 site na 5 tinye ya na 8 na mbụ) echepụtala strategy make-ten. Kpughee ya; kpọọ ya aha; kuziere klas ka ha nwaa ya. Ụzọ akwụkwọ abụghị naanị ụzọ ziri ezi.",
      "using_too_many_manipulatives_at_once": "Iji ọtụtụ manipulatives n'otu oge",
      "a_table_covered_in_4_different_manipul": "Tebụl jupụtara na manipulatives 4 dị iche iche bụ ntọala nke mgbagwoju anya, ọ bụghị differentiation. Họrọ OTU maka ihe ọmụmụ ọ bụla. Ndị ọzọ 11 na ngwaọrụ a dị mma — maka ihe ọmụmụ ndị ọzọ.",
      "forgetting_to_ask_why": "Ichefu ịjụ \"gịnị mere?\"",
      "students_will_arrange_counters_correct": "Ụmụ akwụkwọ ga-ahazi counters n'ụzọ ziri ezi n'ihi na ha eburula nzọụkwụ ahụ n'isi, na-aghọtaghị ihe ọ pụtara. \"Gịnị mere i ji tinye 1 na column nke iri?\" kwesịrị ịbụ ajụjụ gị kacha ajụ.",
      "cleaning_up_too_quickly": "Ihicha ọsọ ọsọ",
      "a_built_construction_is_a_powerful_art": "Ihe owuwu e wuru bụ ihe dị ike — hapụ ya na tebụl ka klas na-ekwu maka ya. Chekwaa ya na Ọbá Akwụkwọ ma ọ bụrụ na ị chọrọ ya echi. Emela ka ụmụ akwụkwọ kwatuo ihe owuwu ha ji ike wuo iji \"dị njikere maka isiokwu na-esote.\"",
      "asking_only_convergent_questions": "Ịjụ naanị ajụjụ convergent",
      "what_is_4_3_has_one_answer_convergent_": "\"Gịnị bụ 4 + 3?\" nwere otu azịza (convergent). \"Gosi m 7 n'ụzọ atọ dị iche\" nwere ọtụtụ (divergent). Prompts divergent na-ekpughe otú ụmụ akwụkwọ si eche echiche — nke bụ assessment dị mkpa.",
