      "growling_dubstep_bass": "Dubstep bass na-agbọ ụja",
      "warm_lo_fi_keys": "Warm lo-fi keys",
      "barry_harris_1929_2021_codified_bebop_": "Barry Harris (1929-2021) hazichara harmony nke bebop. Usoro ya na-eji 6th chords kama 7ths ma na-agbakwụnye diminished passing chords n'etiti ọkwa scale maka iduzi olu nke ọma.",
      "ii_v_i_jazz": "ii-V-I (Jazz)",
      "12_bar_blues": "12-Bar Blues",
      "vi_iv_i_v_emo_alt": "vi-IV-I-V (Emo/Alt)",
      "1st_overtone": "Overtone nke 1",
      "2nd_overtone": "Overtone nke 2",
      "3rd_overtone": "Overtone nke 3",
      "4th_overtone": "Overtone nke 4",
      "5th_overtone": "Overtone nke 5",
      "6th_overtone": "Overtone nke 6",
      "7th_overtone": "Overtone nke 7",
      "attack_time_to_reach_full_volume_decay": "Attack: oge iji ruo volume zuru oke. Decay: oge iji gbadaa na sustain. Sustain: ọkwa volume a na-ejide. Release: oge ọ na-agbaze mgbe a hapụsịrị key.",
      "a_scale_is_an_ordered_set_of_pitches_m": "Scale bụ setịpụ pitches ahaziri ahazi. Modes bụ ntụgharị nke scale nke na-amalite na ọkwa dị iche iche. Nke ọ bụla na-emepụta ọnọdụ mmetụta dị iche.",
      "chords_are_built_by_stacking_intervals": "A na-ewu chords site n'ịkwakọba intervals (3rds). Major na-eji major 3rd + minor 3rd. Minor na-atụgharị ha. Extended chords na-agbakwụnye 7ths, 9ths, na karịa.",
      "kicks_use_a_sine_oscillator_with_a_pit": "Kicks na-eji sine oscillator nwere pitch sweep. Snares na-agwakọta noise (filtered) + tone body. Hi-hats na-eji high-pass filtered noise bursts.",
      "4_4_4_quarter_note_beats_per_bar_most_": "4/4 = quarter-note beats 4 kwa bar (nke a na-ahụkarị). 3/4 = mmetụta waltz. 6/8 = compound duple. 5/4 na 7/8 na-emepụta grooves na-enweghị nhata, mba ọzọ.",
      "keys_arranged_by_ascending_5ths_clockw": "A haziri keys site na 5ths na-arịgo na-eso elekere. Keys agbata obi na-ekekọrịta note 6 n'ime 7. Ịga na-eso elekere na-agbakwụnye sharps; megide elekere na-agbakwụnye flats.",
      "every_musical_sound_contains_overtones": "Ụda egwu ọ bụla nwere overtones n'elu fundamental. Ike ha metụtara na-ekpebi timbre — nke a mere trumpet ji ada dị iche na flute na otu pitch.",
      "an_interval_is_the_distance_between_tw": "Interval bụ anya dị n'etiti pitches abụọ, a na-atụ ya na semitones. Frequency ratio na-ekpebi consonance (ratios dị mfe dịka 3:2 na-ada nke ọma).",
      "plays_chord_notes_one_at_a_time_in_seq": "Na-akpọ notes nke chord otu n'otu n'usoro. Elu = site n'ala gaa n'elu, Ala = site n'elu gaa n'ala. Na-emepụta patterns na-asọ site na chords kwụ ọtọ.",
      "a_filter_removes_frequencies_above_low": "Filter na-ewepụ frequencies dị n'elu (lowpass), n'okpuru (highpass), ma ọ bụ gburugburu (bandpass) cutoff frequency. Resonance (Q) na-abawanye frequencies dị nso na cutoff, na-emepụta peak.",
      "tremolo_periodic_volume_changes_amplit": "Tremolo: mgbanwe volume oge niile (amplitude modulation). Vibrato: mgbanwe pitch oge niile (frequency modulation). A na-eji LFO (Low Frequency Oscillator) achịkwa ha abụọ.",
      "discovered_in_1983_a_noise_burst_feeds": "A chọpụtara ya na 1983. Noise burst na-abanye n'ime delay line dị mkpụmkpụ nke nwere feedback. Delay time na-ekpebi pitch. Filter dị na feedback loop na-achịkwa ìhè na decay. Na-eṣepụ plucked strings n'ụzọ eke.",
      "the_sequencer_is_a_composition_tool_ea": "Sequencer bụ ngwá ọrụ mmebe. Nzọụkwụ ọ bụla na-anọchi anya subdivision nke beat. Ahịrị melody na-edozi pitched notes, drums na-agbakwụnye rhythm. Musical notation na-egosi ihe ị na-emepụta.",
      "notes_on_lines_and_spaces_represent_pi": "Notes dị n'ahịrị na oghere na-anọchi anya pitches. A na-egosi ogologo oge site n'ụdị note: whole (○), half (𝅗𝅥), quarter (♩), eighth (♪). Staff nwere ahịrị 5.",
