      "play_piano_keys_presets": "Kpọọ — piano keys + presets",
      "equal_temperament_12_notes_per_octave_": "Equal temperament: notes 12 kwa octave, ratio 2^(1/12). A4 = 440 Hz; A5 = 880 Hz. Well-Tempered Clavier nke Bach (1722) mere ka ụwa kwenye na nkwekọrịta a. Note ọ bụla ị na-akpọ ebe a dị na grid ahụ.",
      "scales_the_major_minor_modal_grammar": "Scales — grammar major + minor + modal",
      "major_w_w_h_w_w_w_h_minor_w_h_w_w_h_w_": "Major: W-W-H-W-W-W-H. Minor: W-H-W-W-H-W-W. Modes 7 (Ionian, Dorian, Phrygian, Lydian, Mixolydian, Aeolian, Locrian) na-esite n'ịtụgharị interval pattern nke major scale.",
      "chords_stacked_thirds_inversions": "Chords — stacked thirds + inversions",
      "triads_root_third_fifth_major_4_3_semi": "Triads: root + third + fifth. Major (4+3 semitones), minor (3+4), diminished (3+3), augmented (4+4). 7th chords na-agbakwụnye third ọzọ. Pop music = ~chords 6 na-emegharị; jazz na-eji extensions na substitutions.",
      "harmony_pad_voiced_pads_drones": "Harmony Pad — voiced pads + drones",
      "sustained_chord_textures_the_bed_under": "Sustained chord textures — ihe ndina n'okpuru ihe fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ cinematic score ọ bụla. Nwaa iv-V-i na minor, ma ọ bụ i-VI-VII maka mmetụta Hans Zimmer. Drones na fifths na-akwado egwu oge gboo India na omenala bagpipe.",
      "beat_pad_sample_based_drums": "Beat Pad — sample-based drums",
      "most_popular_music_sits_at_4_4_90_130_": "Ọtụtụ egwu ewu ewu dị na 4/4, 90-130 BPM. Hip-hop ~85-95, house 120-130, drum-and-bass ~170 (mmetụta half-time). Kick na 1+3, snare na 2+4 = backbeat — ntọala rock + pop.",
      "theory_the_math_behind_the_sound": "Theory — mgbakọ na mwepụ n'azụ ụda",
      "pythagoras_500_bce_discovered_consonan": "Pythagoras (~500 BCE) chọpụtara consonance site na integer frequency ratios: octave 2:1, fifth 3:2, fourth 4:3. Helmholtz gbasapụrụ nke a na 1862. Ụda = compression waves; egwu = patterns anyị kwetara ịkpọ mara mma.",
