      "fm_synthesis_2": "FM Synthesis",
      "frequency_modulation_fm_synthesis_uses": "Frequency Modulation (FM) synthesis na-eji oscillator otu (modulator) gbanwee frequency nke ọzọ (carrier) ngwa ngwa. Ratio modulator:carrier na-ekpebi harmonic content. Ratios dị mfe (1:1, 2:1, 3:1) na-emepụta harmonic tones. Ratios mgbagwoju anya na-emepụta metallic, bell-like, ma ọ bụ inharmonic sounds. Yamaha DX7 mere ka FM mara amara na 1983.",
      "bright": "Ìhè",
      "fm_mod_depth": "FM modulation depth",
