      "supersaw_controls": "⚡ SuperSaw Controls",
      "supersaw_unison": "SuperSaw / Unison",
      "supersaw_stacks_multiple_sawtooth_osci": "SuperSaw na-akwakọba ọtụtụ sawtooth oscillators nke a detune ntakịrị site na ibe ha. Nke a na-emepụta nnukwu, sara mbara, ụda na-egbuke egbuke — akara EDM, trance, na pop nke oge a. Ọtụtụ voices = na-esiwanye ike mana na-eji CPU karịa. Detuning na-achịkwa ka voices si dị anya na tuning — detune karịa = sara mbara/dịka chorus karịa, ntakịrị = siri ike/na-elekwasị anya karịa.",
