      "the_science_of_chord_progressions": "🔬 Sayensị nke Chord Progressions",
      "chord_progressions_create_emotional_jo": "Chord progressions na-emepụta njem mmetụta. Chord I (tonic) na-adị ka 'ụlọ.' Chord V (dominant) na-emepụta nrụgide nke chọrọ ịlaghachi na I. Chord vi (relative minor) na-agbakwụnye mwute ma ọ bụ omimi. Chord IV (subdominant) na-esi n'ụlọ pụọ nwayọ. A na-atụ anya na I-V-vi-IV progression na-apụta n'ihe karịrị 70% nke abụ pop n'ihi na ọ na-ahazi mmetụta ndị a nke ọma.",
      "roman_numerals_i_ii_iii_iv_v_vi_vii_re": "Ọnụọgụ Roman (I, ii, iii, IV, V, vi, vii°) na-anọchi anya ọkwa scale. Mkpụrụedemede ukwu = major chord. Mkpụrụedemede nta = minor chord.",
