      "i_can_explain_why_this_a_e_m_combinati": "Enwere m ike ịkọwa ihe kpatara nchikota a/e/M ji enye ụdị okirikiri a.",
      "explain_in_your_own_words": "Kọwaa n'okwu nke gị...",
      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Ngwá nnyocha — enweghị akara, enweghị ngosipụta, enweghị ndepụta azịza. T = √(a³/M) dịka Kepler III ebe M dị n'ibu anyanwụ, a n'AU, T n'afọ. E ji Vis-viva maka v na perihelion / aphelion.",
