      "the_minimum_energy_way_to_travel_betwe": "Ụzọ ike kacha nta iji gagharịa n'etiti okirikiri abụọ. Ọkụ abụọ: hapụ okirikiri ime na perihelion nke mbufe, rute okirikiri èzí na aphelion.",
      "challenges_apply_kepler_s_laws": "Ihe Ịma Aka — tinye iwu Kepler n'ọrụ",
      "multi_step_problems_predict_periods_fr": "Nsogbu nwere ọtụtụ nzọụkwụ: buo amụma ogologo oge site n'ọkara ọkpọkọ ukwu, chọpụta ọsọ perihelion na aphelion, gbakọọ Δv okirikiri mbufe. Ọkwa AP Physics 1 + 2.",
