      "asteroid_impact_outcomes": "☄ Nsonaazụ Nkukọ Asteroid",
      "what_size_asteroid_kills_which_level_o": "Asteroid ịdị ukwuu ole na-egbu ọkwa ndụ ole? Tụnyere site na obere nkume ruo onye gburu dinosaur.",
      "size_m": "Ịdị ukwuu (m)",
      "atmospheric_entry_destroys_most_rocks_": "Ọnụ ụzọ ikuku na-ebibi ọtụtụ nkume < 5m. Chelyabinsk 2013 (20m) gbajiri windo mana o nweghị olulu. Tunguska 1908 (50m) kwatuo 2000km² nke ọhịa. Chicxulub 66Ma (10km) gburu dinosaur.",
      "coronal_mass_ejection": "⚡ Mwepụta Ibu Corona",
      "a_cme_blasts_billions_of_tons_of_plasm": "CME na-agbapụta ijeri tọn plasma site n'Anyanwụ. Ụbọchị ole na ole ka o gasịrị, ọ nwere ike ibute ìhè ndịda mara mma + ọdịda GPS.",
