      "drive_30_min_from_city_lights_maine_is": "Kwọọ nkeji 30+ site n'ìhè obodo. Maine jupụtara na ha. Katahdin Woods and Waters bụ ebe nchekwa eluigwe ọchịchịrị a kwadoro.",
      "most_important_tool_dark_sky_light_pol": "Ngwá ọrụ kacha mkpa: eluigwe gbara ọchịchịrị. Mmetọ ìhè na-ehichapụ pasent 90 nke kpakpando. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM na AMC Maine Woods bụ ebe Eluigwe Ọchịchịrị Ụwa Niile a kwadoro; Acadia na Baxter na-enyekwa eluigwe ọchịchịrị mara mma.",
      "how_stars_die": "⚱ Ka Kpakpando Si Anwụ",
