      "how_a_star_dies_depends_almost_entirel": "Ka kpakpando si anwụ dabere fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ kpamkpam n'ibu ya mbụ. Oke n'etiti kpakpando neutron + oghere ojii adịghị doro anya (oke Tolman-Oppenheimer-Volkoff ~2-3 M☉ maka ihe fọdụrụ).",
