      "distances_jump_in_scale_km_to_au_to_ly": "Anya na-awụli n'ọtụtụ: km ruo AU ruo ly ruo ijeri ly. Nzọụkwụ ọ bụla bụ ~ugboro 10,000-100,000 karịa. Nyocha kpakpando na-ebi n'ọtụtụ log.",
      "maine_night_sky_by_season": "🌲 Eluigwe Abalị Maine Site n'Oge",
      "maine_has_world_class_dark_skies_what_": "Maine nwere eluigwe ọchịchịrị kacha mma n'ụwa. Ihe a ga-achọ n'oge ọ bụla.",
      "maine_has_fantastic_dark_skies_especia": "Maine nwere eluigwe ọchịchịrị dị ịtụnanya — karịsịa n'ugwu obodo. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM na AMC Maine Woods bụ ebe Eluigwe Ọchịchịrị Ụwa Niile a kwadoro; Acadia, Allagash, Baxter, na Cobscook gbakwara ọchịchịrị nke ọma. Abalị oyi dị ogologo + dị ọcha nke ukwuu.",
