      "space_exploration_is_in_a_renaissance_": "Nyocha mbara igwe nọ na mmalitegharị. Mba ọhụrụ (India, Japan, UAE), ụlọ ọrụ nkeonwe ọhụrụ (SpaceX, Blue Origin), ọrụ ọhụrụ (Europa Clipper, Artemis, JWST). Lelie elu — ma ṅaa ntị.",
