      "maine_utc_5_est_or_utc_4_edt_london_ut": "Maine: UTC-5 (EST) ma ọ bụ UTC-4 (EDT). Lọndọn: UTC+0 (GMT) ma ọ bụ UTC+1 (BST). Japan: UTC+9.",
