      "drop_paint_spin_watch_it_fling_outward": "Tụsa agba, tụgharịa, lee ka ọ na-agbasa n'èzí n'ụdị gburugburu. Damien Hirst nwetara nde ego site n'ire ihe osise ntụgharị. Otu physics ahụ dịka igwe mmiri salad; F = mω²r.",
